<tr><td>PII Detection</td><td><code>#Microsoft.Skills.Text.PIIDetectionSkill</code></td></tr>
<tr><td>Custom (Web API)</td><td><code>#Microsoft.Skills.Custom.WebApiSkill</code></td></tr></table>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><b>Context paths:</b> <code>/document</code>, <code>/document/content</code>, <code>/document/normalized_images/*</code>, <code>/document/pages/*</code></p>`},
  {d:'d6', title:'Index Fields & Data Types', content:`<table class="cs-table"><tr><th>Attribute</th><th>For</th></tr>
<tr><td><code>searchable</code></td><td>Full-text search (tokenized). Use when users type free-text queries.</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>filterable</code></td><td>$filter expressions. Use for exact match, range, comparison (e.g., <code>rating ge 4</code>).</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>sortable</code></td><td>$orderby. Use when users sort by this field (price, date).</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>facetable</code></td><td>Faceted navigation. Use for sidebar counts: "Hotels (42), Restaurants (18)".</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>retrievable</code></td><td>Returned in results. Set false to hide internal fields.</td></tr>
<tr><td><code>key</code></td><td>Unique doc ID (exactly one per index).</td></tr></table>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><b>Types:</b> Edm.String, Edm.Int32/64, Edm.Double, Edm.Boolean, Edm.DateTimeOffset, Edm.GeographyPoint, Edm.ComplexType, Collection(Edm.Single) = vector</p>`},
  {d:'d6', title:'Vector & Semantic Search', content:`<p><b>Vector search:</b> Store embeddings in <code>Collection(Edm.Single)</code> fields.</p>
<table class="cs-table" style="margin-top:8px"><tr><th>Algorithm</th><th>Type</th></tr>
<tr><td>HNSW</td><td>Fast approximate (default)</td></tr>
<tr><td>Exhaustive KNN</td><td>Slow exact, 100% recall</td></tr></table>
<table class="cs-table" style="margin-top:8px"><tr><th>Metric</th><th>Use</th></tr>
<tr><td>cosine</td><td>Most text embeddings</td></tr>
<tr><td>euclidean</td><td>Distance-based</td></tr>
<tr><td>dotProduct</td><td>Normalized vectors</td></tr>
<tr><td>hamming</td><td>Binary vectors only</td></tr></table>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><b>Semantic:</b> <code>queryType=semantic&semanticConfiguration=name</code>. Provides captions + answers. Config: titleField, prioritizedContentFields, prioritizedKeywordsFields.</p>
<p style="margin-top:8px"><b>Hybrid:</b> Text + vector combined via Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF).</p>`},
  {d:'d6', title:'Scoring Profiles & Suggesters', content:`<table class="cs-table"><tr><th>Function</th><th>Boosts By</th></tr>
<tr><td>magnitude</td><td>Numeric value (rating, clicks)</td></tr>
<tr><td>freshness</td><td>Date recency</td></tr>
<tr><td>distance</td><td>Geographic proximity</td></tr>
<tr><td>tag</td><td>Matching tags from query param</td></tr></table>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><b>Interpolation:</b> linear (default), constant, quadratic, logarithmic. ⚠️ quadratic + logarithmic NOT allowed for tag.</p>
<p style="margin-top:8px"><b>Aggregation:</b> sum (default), average, minimum, maximum, firstMatching</p>
<p style="margin-top:12px"><b>Suggesters:</b> Enable autocomplete + suggestions. <code>searchMode: analyzingInfixMatching</code>. String fields only. One per index.</p>
<p style="margin-top:8px"><b>Synonym maps:</b> <code>"hotel, motel, inn"</code> or <code>"US => USA"</code>. One map per field, max 5,000 rules.</p>`},
  {d:'d6', title:'Numbers to Remember', content:`<table class="cs-table"><tr><th>What</th><th>Value</th></tr>
<tr><td>AI Search free tier</td><td>50 MB storage, 3 indexes</td></tr>
